---

<section class="min-h-screen flex items-center bg-cream relative overflow-hidden" aria-label="Introducción">
  
  <!-- Fondo sutil -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[60%] h-[60%] bg-gradient-to-bl from-sage/[0.03] to-transparent"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-[15%] left-[5%] w-[300px] h-[300px] border border-sage/[0.06] rounded-full"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-editorial relative z-10 pt-8 pb-16">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
      
      <!-- Contenido izquierda -->
      <div class="max-w-xl">
        
        <div class="mb-6" data-reveal>
          <span class="label-section">Psicóloga General Sanitaria</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="title-section mb-6" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="100">
          Encuentra tu<br/>
          <em>equilibrio emocional</em>
        </h1>

        <p class="text-body mb-8 max-w-md" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="200">
          Soy María Ángeles Mata. Un espacio seguro donde explorar tu mundo interior con acompañamiento profesional y respaldado por evidencia científica.
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-8" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="300">
          <span class="tag">Terapia Individual</span>
          <span class="tag">Pareja</span>
          <span class="tag">15 años experiencia</span>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mb-10" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="400">
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-sage">
            <span>Reservar consulta</span>
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M17.25 8.75L21 12m0 0l-3.75 3.25M21 12H3" />
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="#servicios" class="btn btn-outline">Explorar servicios</a>
        </div>

        <div class="flex items-center gap-8 pt-6 border-t border-border" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="500">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-sage" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray">Colegiada AN-01452</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-sage" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M16.5 10.5V6.75a4.5 4.5 0 10-9 0v3.75m-.75 11.25h10.5a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25v-6.75a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25-2.25H6.75a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25 2.25v6.75a2.25 2.25 0 002.25 2.25z" />
            </svg>
            <span class="text-xs text-gray">100% confidencial</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Imagen derecha -->
      <div class="relative lg:pl-8" data-reveal="right" data-reveal-delay="200">
        <div class="relative">
          <!-- Marco -->
          <div class="absolute -inset-3 border border-border rounded-xl"></div>
          
          <!-- Imagen -->
          <div class="relative aspect-[4/5] rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
            <img
              src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1573497620053-ea5300f94f21?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=85"
              alt="María Ángeles Mata"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
              width="600"
              height="750"
              loading="eager"
            />
          </div>

          <!-- Badge experiencia -->
          <div class="absolute -top-3 -right-3 bg-sage text-cream px-4 py-2 rounded-lg shadow-md" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="500">
            <p class="text-xs font-medium">+15 años</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Badge ubicación -->
          <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -left-4 bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-lg border border-border" data-reveal data-reveal-delay="600">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
              <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-sage/10 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-sage" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 10.5a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 10.5c0 7.142-7.5 11.25-7.5 11.25S4.5 17.642 4.5 10.5a7.5 7.5 0 1115 0z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-[10px] text-gray uppercase tracking-wide">Córdoba</p>
                <p class="text-xs font-medium text-charcoal">C/ Rodríguez Sánchez, 22</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
